and then stand there and say,

78
00:04:00,615 --> 00:04:03,618
"Gurp. Gurp. Gurp."

79
00:04:03,701 --> 00:04:04,661
I don't know.

80
00:04:04,744 --> 00:04:07,538
I can't picture it.
I've been hot my whole life.

81
