Sorry, who is this conversation for again?

82
00:04:09,374 --> 00:04:10,250
It's for you.

83
00:04:10,333 --> 00:04:12,293
I believe in you, nerd boy.

84
00:04:12,377 --> 00:04:16,839
If you can teach me and Jason ethics,
you can teach anybody.

85
00:04:17,423 --> 00:04:18,383
Thanks.

86
00:04:18,466 --> 00:04:22,220
