your first paragraph?

116
00:05:44,343 --> 00:05:48,222
"Everyone in this story sucks
and belongs in the Bad Place.

117
00:05:49,390 --> 00:05:54,604
The thief is bad, the officer chasing him
is bad, all the whiny prostitutes are bad,

118
