because that makes you more French.

124
00:06:14,332 --> 00:06:15,792
Okay, sure,

125
00:06:15,875 --> 00:06:19,712
but philosophy is about questioning things
you take for granted

126
00:06:19,796 --> 00:06:22,048
and I don't think you're doing that.

127
00:06:22,131 --> 00:06:24,258
I mean, "I personally know

128
00:06:24,342 --> 00:06:27,345
Victor Hugo is in the Bad Place,
being tortured.

129
00:06:27,428 --> 00:06:29,347
He's a real wuss, too.

130
00:06:29,430 --> 00:06:32,225
