and he has no voice in this relationship.

148
00:07:26,821 --> 00:07:29,323
Right, Jason? Good.
Now, where were we?

149
00:07:31,868 --> 00:07:33,202
Just heard that.

150
00:07:33,286 --> 00:07:35,371
Okay, fine. I'll leave.

151
00:07:35,997 --> 00:07:40,001
