you're engaging with the material.

152
00:07:40,084 --> 00:07:42,295
Like with the trolley problem.

153
00:07:42,378 --> 00:07:44,380
That was just tricky, that's all.

154
00:07:44,464 --> 00:07:46,340
Why don't you tell me the right answer?

155
00:07:46,424 --> 00:07:48,843
That's what's so great
about the trolley problem,

156
00:07:48,926 --> 00:07:50,887
